outputs.output_descr: The project seeks to enhance technical and institutional capacity of the country to mainstream climate change concerns in national development plans and policies by enabling Swaziland to prepare and submit its Second National Communication to the UNFCCC.

project_descr: Enabling Activities for the Preparation of Swaziland's Second National Communication to the UNFCCC
project_title: GEF PIMS 3352 SWAZI MSP Swaziland's SNC.
